      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the Hawaii Climate Institute at the University of Hawaii.  Transfers the functions of the International Pacific Research Center at the School of Ocean and Earth Science and Technology at the University of Hawaii at Manoa to the Hawaii Climate Institute.  Establishes positions.  Appropriates funds."
